{"tid":1322893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（突發奇想）香城online移動防彈板構思","createTime":"2019-07-16T05:32:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T07:45:33.000Z","uid":103349,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"342b8ba1cce536ad493176b8c59618aabfa30809","tid":1322893,"uid":103349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:32:53.000Z","msg":"見到好多防具post主要都係圍繞住防噴霧同煙 <br />\n<br />\n但係下次極有可能開槍<br />\n<br />\n希望提醒下各位做好萬全準備 唔好流血<br />\n<br />\n想法如下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cikhgtp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcikhgtp.jpg&h=ad976da7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可以郁既壁報板 唔洗多 放係最前線已經好有用 可以阻擋對面視線 就算咩都唔加都可以減輕物理攻擊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QbSjuMm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQbSjuMm.jpg&h=0cd8a880&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係壁報板背面可安裝門把 方便移動防線<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Nftn8w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Nftn8w.jpg&h=d569c475&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前面更可安裝木板加強防禦力<br />\n<br />\n雖然想法幼稚 <br />\n但係咁多位義士 共勉之"},{"pid":"431bf1195a087bcc451fad32f50ad892149f5340","tid":1322893,"uid":197563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:01:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba07eda3e591ac86749f636b48e2936bf291b469","tid":1322893,"uid":240670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:11:07.000Z","msg":"點解無人用航拍機監察差佬部署 兵力分怖等等?"},{"pid":"d3b60eec7f574f450ea0eb84880b8dcbc02b66fd","tid":1322893,"uid":258192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:37:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0a5a83070fcbde1f8e7f24d6ce766032383c4447","tid":1322893,"uid":22463,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:41:26.000Z","msg":"零便攜性 算9數"},{"pid":"ecf68bae023a29f3bb83e42a793ad41648dfb0d2","tid":1322893,"uid":193436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"